ain\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?fit=3143%2C4400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"3143,4400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banana Essay\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-660\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?resize=262%2C367&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"262\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?w=3143&amp;ssl=1 3143w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Banana-Essay.png?w=2400&amp;ssl=1 2400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 262px) 100vw, 262px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/p>\n<p>There are only a few cards in the entire game that give you 5 or more actions on your turn, and they all occur Junior or Senior year. This makes this Essay extremely difficult to play, which was the intention. However, I wanted to make the card a little bit easier to play. At 4 consecutive relax actions, you still have to go out of your way to play it, but it can be done if you are determined to do so.<\/p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"581\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/07\/new-essay-mechanic\/wrong-name\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=3143%2C4400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"3143,4400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wrong Name\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-581\" src=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=322%2C450&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"322\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?w=3143&amp;ssl=1 3143w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w, https:\/\/i1.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/07\/Wrong-Name.png?w=2400&amp;ssl=1 2400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 322px) 100vw, 322px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/>\u00a0 \u00a0<img data-attachment-id=\"661\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/jorgezhang.com\/2018\/08\/adjusting-cards-part-six\/wrong-name-2\/#main\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=3143%2C4400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"3143,4400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Wrong Name\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?fit=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-661\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=326%2C456&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"326\" height=\"456\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?w=3143&amp;ssl=1 3143w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=768%2C1075&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?resize=731%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 731w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/jorgezhang.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/08\/Wrong-Name.png?w=2400&amp;ssl=1 2400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \